AGRICULTURE CODE

a person required to be licensed who is released by a final judgment
of a bankruptcy court from the legal duty to satisfy the claim paid
by the department.
(e) The amount to be reimbursed under this section shall be one
and one-half times the amount of the claim paid if the person
required to reimburse the department was not licensed on the date on
which the transaction forming the base of the claim occurred.
